ications. It is also involved in the construction, business support, industrial material distribution, semiconductor apparel manufacturing, baking, hospital, education, information and communication, investment, and money trust activities. The company was formerly known as Hynix Semiconductor Inc. and changed its name to SK hynix Inc. in March 2012. SK hynix Inc. was founded in 1949 and is headquartered in Icheon-si, South Korea.", "financialCurrency": "KRW", "totalRevenue": 132083674513408, "grossProfits": 78783314919424, "operatingIncome": null, "netIncomeToCommon": 75157288779776, "country": "South Korea"}, "currency": "KRW", "usd_rate": 0.0006703311228193343}}